<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= seo ? seo.title : 'Agrim Classes' %></title>
<meta name="description" content="<%= seo ? seo.desc : 'Best Coaching Institute in Deoli' %>">
<meta name="keywords" content="<%= seo ? seo.keywords : 'education, coaching' %>">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css?v=1.1">
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

<script src="header.js"></script>
    <my-header></my-header>

    <section class="breadcrumb-area">

        <div class="shape-globe">
            <svg width="60" height="60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFA500" stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
                <path d="M2 12h20"></path>
                <path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z">
                </path>
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="shape-loop">
            <svg width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="#C4C6E5" stroke-width="12"
                stroke-linecap="round">
                <path d="M30,20 Q60,5 80,40 T50,90 T20,60" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="shape-scribbles">
            <svg width="80" height="100" viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="#FFC07F" stroke-width="3">
                <path d="M80,10 Q90,20 85,30 T90,50" />
                <path d="M60,15 Q70,5 75,25 T80,40" />
                <path d="M90,5 Q100,15 95,25 T100,45" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <div class="container">
            <div class="banner-content align-left">
                <span class="sub-heading">Agrim Classes</span>
                <h1 class="page-title">Pre - Foundation</h1>
                <ul class="breadcrumb-list">
                    <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="separator"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></li>
                    <li>Batches</li>
                    <li class="separator"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></li>
                    <li class="active">Pre Foundation</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

<section class="pre-found-hero">
    <div class="hero-shapes">
        <div class="shape s-1"></div>
        <div class="shape s-2"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content text-center">
            <span class="badge-pill-glow">Class 6th to 10th</span>
            <h1 class="hero-title">Igniting the Spark of <br><span class="text-gradient">Genius</span></h1>
            <p class="hero-desc">
                The journey to IIT-JEE, NEET, and Olympiads doesn't start in Class 11. 
                It begins now. We transform raw curiosity into structured brilliance, 
                building a foundation so strong that future success becomes inevitable.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-btns">
                <a href="#journey" class="btn-primary">View the Roadmap</a>
                <a href="contact.html" class="btn-secondary">Download Brochure</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="why-early-section">
    <div class="" style="margin-left: 70px; margin-right: 70px;">
        <div class="section-header text-center mb-5">
            <span class="sub-heading">The Advantage</span>
            <h2>Why Start Early?</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="early-grid">
            <div class="early-card">
                <div class="icon-box ib-blue"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i></div>
                <h4>High IQ & Logic</h4>
                <p>Developing critical thinking skills young makes complex problems look easy later.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="early-card">
                <div class="icon-box ib-orange"><i class="fas fa-hourglass-half"></i></div>
                <h4>Stress-Free Class 11</h4>
                <p>By covering basics early, students don't feel the "sudden jump" in difficulty in Class 11.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="early-card">
                <div class="icon-box ib-purple"><i class="fas fa-medal"></i></div>
                <h4>Olympiad Success</h4>
                <p>Specific training for NSO, IMO, and NTSE to build a profile of achievements.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="early-card">
                <div class="icon-box ib-green"><i class="fas fa-school"></i></div>
                <h4>School Topper</h4>
                <p>We cover school syllabus in depth, ensuring they stay ahead of their class effortlessly.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="journey-section" id="journey">
    <div class="">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="main-heading">The Roadmap to Excellence</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="journey-wrapper">
            
            <div class="journey-item">
                <div class="j-content">
                    <span class="step-badge">Phase 1</span>
                    <h3>The Awakening (Class 6-8)</h3>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Focus: Curiosity & Basics</strong><br>
                        We transition students from rote learning to "Why and How". 
                        We introduce them to the magic of Science and the logic of Maths 
                        through experiments and visual learning.
                    </p>
                    <div class="tags">
                        <span>Foundation Builder</span>
                        <span>Basic Olympiads</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="j-visual">
                    <div class="visual-circle circle-1"><i class="fas fa-seedling"></i></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="journey-item item-reverse">
                <div class="j-content">
                    <span class="step-badge">Phase 2</span>
                    <h3>The Acceleration (Class 9)</h3>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Focus: Concepts & Application</strong><br>
                        The intensity increases. We introduce concepts that bridge the gap 
                        between school syllabus and competitive exams. Students start 
                        solving complex problems with ease.
                    </p>
                    <div class="tags">
                        <span>NTSE Stage-1 Prep</span>
                        <span>Scientific Temper</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="j-visual">
                    <div class="visual-circle circle-2"><i class="fas fa-running"></i></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="journey-item">
                <div class="j-content">
                    <span class="step-badge">Phase 3</span>
                    <h3>The Launchpad (Class 10)</h3>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Focus: Board Mastery & Competitive Edge</strong><br>
                        The final year of pre-foundation. We align board exam preparation 
                        with advanced competitive strategies. Students are made "JEE/NEET Ready".
                    </p>
                    <div class="tags">
                        <span>Board Topper</span>
                        <span>Career Selection</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="j-visual">
                    <div class="visual-circle circle-3"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i></div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="boosters-section">
    <div class="" style="margin-left: 70px; margin-right: 70px;">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="main-heading">The Agrim Advantage</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="boosters-grid">
            <div class="booster-card card-red">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i></div>
                <h4>Expert<br>Mentors</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="booster-card card-green">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-layer-group"></i></div>
                <h4>Small Batch<br>(Special 20)</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="booster-card card-dark-blue">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i></div>
                <h4>Doubt<br>Resolution</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="booster-card card-light-blue">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-laptop"></i></div>
                <h4>Hybrid<br>Learning</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="booster-card card-grey">
                <div class="icon-wrapper"><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i></div>
                <h4>Weekly<br>Testing</h4>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="creative-cta-box">
    <div class="" style="margin-left: 70px; margin-right: 70px;">
        <div class="cta-inner">
            <div class="cta-text">
                <h2>Secure Their Future Today</h2>
                <p>Limited seats available for the upcoming Pre-Foundation batch.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-btn">
                <a href="contact.html" class="btn-white">Apply for Admission</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<my-footer></my-footer>


<script src="footer.js"></script>
</body>